FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://api.soccersapi.com/v2.2/

# soccersapi

SoccersAPI is a RESTful service for soccer data sport. It is a PAID service with low price (started with $30 per month). Note that in order to access Soccer's API you must purchase related packages. Please contact us if you have any problem.

## Countries List [/countries/{?user,token,t}]

+ Parameters
    + user - YOUR_USER
    + token - YOUR_TOKEN
    + t - list


### List All Countries [GET] 

+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /countries
 
    
    + Body

 
