## Country Info [/countries/{?user,token,t,id}]    

+ Parameters
    + user - YOUR_USER
    + token - YOUR_TOKEN
    + t - info
    + id - COUNTRY_ID
    
### Get country info by ID [GET]


+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /countries

    + Body

   {
        "id": 43482,
        "name": "Afghanistan",
        "continent": "Asia",
        "sub_region": "Southern Asia",
        "long": "66.02528381347656",
        "lat": "33.833248138427734",
        "image": "/countries/43482.png"
    } 
 

